"RPMベースのシステムでは`nfs-utils`パッケージを、DEBベースのシステムでは`nfs-common`"
"パッケージをインストールしてください。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The NFS server service should not be enabled in systemd since that will conflict with "
"DRBD Reactor's ability to manage the service. Disable the `nfs-server` service and "
"verify that it has been disabled using the following commands:"
