#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"After running the command above, you will have a highly available 2GiB NVMe-oF target "
"created in your cluster that is discoverable on the IP address used in the command. "
"The target will be backed by a DRBD device managed by LINSTOR. The DRBD resource was "
"created by LINSTOR in the `nvmeof_group` resource group. The DRBD Reactor "
"configuration files created by the above command can be found in `/etc/drbd-reactor.d/"
"`."
msgstr ""
"上記のコマンドを実行した後、クラスター内に作成された高い可用性を持つ2GiBのNVMe-oFター"
